  "title": {
    "en": "Table 4.1: Expenditure on welfare schemes and activities against total receipts (2019-20 to 2022-23)"
  },
  "summary": {
    "en": "Year-wise total receipts and expenditure on welfare schemes by the Delhi BOCW Welfare Board from 2019-20 to 2022-23. Expenditure as a percentage of total receipts ranged between 9.53 and 11.33 per cent except in 2021-22 when ex-gratia payments under Covid-19 relief inflated the ratio to 128.11 per cent. Total receipts over four years were ₹ 1774.42 crore against which welfare expenditure was ₹ 605.02 crore."
  },
  "unit": "₹ in crore",
  "source": {
    "en": "Delhi BOCW Welfare Board records"
  },
